rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Naza about Mira's plant life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Naza if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Naza about the weather in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Naza about the weather in Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0001
rows.name:
As Cavern Clan prisoner, I was forced to mine caves
in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0002
rows.name:
Inside one cave, I saw strange cactus.
It turned silver when rains came.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0003
rows.name:
Once I was freed, I did not forget cactus.
I asked Nopon science person what it was.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0004
rows.name:
Plant is known as myuena cactus.
It is very rare. Can be sold for high price.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0005
rows.name: It is worth searching for if you visit Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0008
rows.name:
Grr! Why do they not take in Mira's soil?
What must I do to gather Old Ones and...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0009
rows.name: ...Hmm? Is something troubling me? Bah.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0010
rows.name:
I am grateful to you, Earth alien.
But this is not your concern.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0011
rows.name:
Some matters are too secret to share.
You must earn my trust first.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0016
rows.name:
Intense heat waves muddle your mind.
Make it harder to put power into attacks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0017
rows.name:
Sandstorms impair vision.
Make it harder to hit enemies with firearms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Oblivia's weather causes many headaches.
But if you are prepared, you will survive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0019
rows.name:
Carry anticlimate augments. Wear proper gear.
Such preparation can save you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0025
rows.name: Strong winds kick up many spores in Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0026
rows.name: Spores block out your vision.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0027
rows.name:
It is like spores are warding off travelers.
Forbidding us to enter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0028
rows.name:
Prone have very old saying:
"Heed nature's warning. Or die nature's death."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0029
rows.name:
You should heed warning of Sylvalum.
Or at least travel with care.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Naza about Mira's plant life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Naza about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL1031
rows.name: Ask Naza about Mira.

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1001
rows.name: I sought Mon'barac's counsel on Great Tree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1002
rows.name:
If we plant more Great Trees, we could create forests
like on Prone homeworld. Forests that are welcoming
havens for Old Ones.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1003
rows.name:
This would complete my mission as Protector of
Great Tree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1004
rows.name:
Maybe I should apologize to Mon'barac for punching
him in face...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1009
rows.name: Something here pulls at me...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1010
rows.name:
If Nopon are only native Miran people,
where did ruins come from?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1011
rows.name:
What happened to those who built ruins?
Where are they now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1012
rows.name:
Something happened before we arrived.
Something that ripped this world out of history.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG1013
rows.name:
But you have seen more of Mira than me.
Do you feel same?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_JNK1010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_JNK2020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Naza about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0030
rows.name:
Foolish Yun'tonam still does not understand gravity of
eating Great Tree![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0031
rows.name: "Grow another," he says. But we have no seeds here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0032
rows.name: ...Hmm? Why am I also being hard on Mon'barac?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045601_MSG0033
rows.name:
Sins of one Orphean are sins of all!
Mon'barac must also show repentance.[ST:wait ]
